[2026-04-04 18:26:00] [stdout] reason + Rousseauian co-
[2026-04-04 18:26:00] [stdout] authorship, operationalized via
[2026-04-04 18:26:00] [stdout] explainability mandates and
[2026-04-04 18:26:00] [stdout] public-facing oversight
[2026-04-04 18:26:00] [stdout] dashboards.
[2026-04-04 18:26:00] [stdout] Global Reach
